        <p class="left"><strong>Specialities:</strong> CSS/SASS, Git, HTML, JavaScript/jQuery, object-oriented programming, Rails, Ruby, Sinatra, Sublime Text, SQL</p>
      </div>

      <div class="skills_module_right">
